email_subject: Save an extra $50 of Compaq's powerful iPaq H3835! (CNET SHOPPER)
email_body: The body of the email is in HTML format and contains promotional content for various products such as the Sony CLIE PEG-NR70V, Compaq iPaq H3835, Handspring Treo 90, Palm m515, Sharp Zaurus SL-5500, and Compaq iPaq H3850. It includes images, links to products, and special offers like free shipping and price discounts. The email also contains links for managing subscriptions and advertisements.
